---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About TerraTAC">
  <section class="container mx-auto w-full py-8 px-4 sm:py-16 sm:px-8 overflow-x-hidden">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">About TerraTAC</h1>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 text-center">TerraTAC is dedicated to providing high-quality tactical and survival gear for professionals and enthusiasts alike. Our mission is to ensure you are always prepared, equipped, and protected, no matter the challenge.</p>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 text-center">We source only the best products, rigorously tested for reliability and performance. Whether you are in the field, on a mission, or exploring the outdoors, TerraTAC has your back.</p>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-center">Thank you for choosing TerraTAC. Stay safe, stay prepared.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
      <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="British Flag" class="h-10 w-10 sm:h-14 sm:w-14" />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
